1) On wp-local machine 
   - backup db
   - run rebaselinks on the wp-content folder
   - git push

2) On another machine
   - git pull
   - backup the framework settings to the rebaselinks directory
   - run the rebaselinks on the ./ folder
   - git push
   - ftp the wp-content folder to live

3) On live
   - Using add from server plugin, update the media library
   - restore the db
   - restore the framework settings
   